- ✅ Build verification

### Security
- ✅ SQL injection vulnerabilities
- ✅ Cross-site scripting (XSS)
- ✅ Authentication bypasses
- ✅ Dependency vulnerabilities
- ✅ Secrets detection
- ✅ OWASP Top 10 issues
- ✅ React/Next.js specific security patterns

### Performance
